<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span> صحيح - <span class="c2">((الصحيحة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٤٣٢)</span> , <span class="c2">((غاية المرام)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢٩٢)</span> , <span class="c2">((صحيح أبي داود)</span>) <span class="c2">(١٧٥٩)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>